# Theming and Styling System

## Main Styling Files

### Core Styles
- **[styles.css](mdc:styles.css)** - Main application styles (29KB, comprehensive styling)
- **[theme.css](mdc:theme.css)** - Base theme variables and colors

### Component-Specific Styles
- **[quiz-builder.css](mdc:quiz-builder.css)** - Quiz builder tool styling (19KB)
- **[topic-builder.css](mdc:topic-builder.css)** - Topic builder tool styling (11KB)
- **[theme-designer.css](mdc:theme-designer.css)** - Theme designer tool styling (10KB)

## Theme System

### Pre-built Themes
Available in **[themes/](mdc:themes)** directory:
- **[light-theme.css](mdc:themes/light-theme.css)** - Light color scheme
- **[default-dark.css](mdc:themes/default-dark.css)** - Dark color scheme
- **[ocean-blue.css](mdc:themes/ocean-blue.css)** - Blue-themed design
- **[test.css](mdc:themes/test.css)** - Test theme for development

### Theme Designer Tool
**[theme-designer.html](mdc:theme-designer.html)** + **[theme-designer.js](mdc:theme-designer.js)** provides a visual interface for:
- Customizing color schemes
- Adjusting typography
- Modifying component styles
- Real-time preview of changes

### Theme Documentation
Detailed theming guide available in **[THEME_DESIGNER_README.md](mdc:THEME_DESIGNER_README.md)**.

## Responsive Design

The application uses responsive design principles:
- Mobile-first approach
- Flexible grid layouts
- Scalable typography
- Touch-friendly interface elements

## CSS Architecture

- CSS custom properties (variables) for theme consistency
- Modular component-based styling
- Consistent naming conventions
- Responsive breakpoints for different screen sizes

